    "body": "As far as i understand\r\nin the most mininal configuration we only need p2p-ports and grpc-port on **beacon** node?\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>## beacon-chain\r\ntcp:4000\r\ntcp:13000\r\nudp:12000</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\nAll other ports are optional\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>## beacon-chain\r\ntcp:8080\tOK\t\t--disable-monitoring\r\ntcp:3500\tOK\t\t--disable-grpc-gateway\r\n\r\n## validator\r\ntcp:8081\t???\t\t(--disable-monitoring ERRO[0000] flag provided but not defined)\r\ntcp:7000\t???\r\ntcp:7500\t???\t\t(--disable-grpc-gateway ERRO[0000] flag provided but not defined)\r\n\r\n## slasher\r\ntcp:8082\t???\t\t(--disable-monitoring ERRO[0000] flag provided but not defined)\r\ntcp:4002\t???\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>",
