    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Looks like a few things to do here:\r\n- The disable-monitoring flag doesn't work on validator or slasher\r\n- Validator port 7000 is the validator's gRPC server, used for querying information in the UI \r\n- Validator port 7500 is the gRPC gateway, same usage as port 7500. This should also be disabled with disable-grpc-gateway\r\n- Slasher port 4002 is the slasher's gRPC server, it does not have a flag to disable it at the moment. \r\n\r\nHere's our contributing guide: https://docs.prylabs.network/docs/contribute/contribution-guidelines/\r\n\r\nFeel free to ping me or anyone on the team in discord, I can help point you in the right direction to register and use these flags.",
